Internship at the Toronto Dominion Bank Jan 2024 - April 2024
item.description: Reflection on my internship at TD I recently interned at TD Bank, one of the leading banks in Canada. Here are my thoughts on my experience and what I learned. There is a lot that I have learned, and I have tried to list some of the major items below. All thoughts are my own and I have redacted any personal information and team information. The main goal for all my blogs is to provide a personal reflection of different years of my life.
